let text: &[u8] = b"word, test.";
let input = ByteInput { text, only_utf8: false };
let at = InputAt { pos: 4, c: Char(100), byte: Some(b'w'), len: 4 };
let empty = InstEmptyLook { goto: InstPtr, look: prog::EmptyLook::WordBoundaryAscii };
let c1 = input.previous_char(at);
let c2 = input.next_char(at);
assert_eq!(c1.is_word_byte() != c2.is_word_byte(), input.is_empty_match(at, &empty));
